         <abstract id="aspace_ec31617ad8df4914542056c9701a9b3c">The collection contains the personal and professional papers of Ronnie Gilbert, singer, playwrite, psychotherapist, narrator of numerous documentary films, feminist, and global peace worker. Also includes extensive audiovisual materials documenting concerts, albums, and interviews with Ronnie Gilbert and others.</abstract>
